    //Mail
    "blue704.JojaCC_JojaMoneyRewardMail.text": "Welcome to Pelican Town!^^JojaCo has decided to build a new Joja Civic Center in your town. However, we need a little help from you. As the new local farmer we hope that you will be able to help us stock and fill our new Civic Center to the brim with local products. Sadly we will only be able to allow Joja Members to have access to this new building, but don't worry. We are here to help!^^Included with this letter we are awarding you a 5000G bonus so that you can go and purchase that membership today and get started right away on the new Joja Civic Center. We are looking forward to seeing great things from you @!^^Join Us. Thrive",
    "blue704.JojaCC_JojaMoneyRewardMail.title": "Joja Money Reward Mail",
    "blue704.JojaCC_EarlyJojaMembershipDiscountMail.text": "Welcome to Pelican Town!^^We are writing to you from JojaCo to let you in on a special offer. For a limited time only you can purchase a new Joja Membership for only 1000G!^^This may seem like a lot but not only do you receive special discounts from JojaMart with a Joja Membership, but JojaCo is planning something special for your town when the next Joja Membership is purchased.^^Here at JojaCo we have heard the lament that commmunity is no longer a part of small town life. Well we hope to change that by building a new Joja Civic Center! Our hope is that the Joja Civic Center will be a place where people can gather for communtiy as well as open small town shops, and Pelican Town has been selected to pioneer this new idea. So stop on by your local JojaMart and purchase your new Joja Membership today!^^Join Us. Thrive^^Offer only applicable for the next Joja Membership purchased. After that price will increase to the standard 5000G.",
    "blue704.JojaCC_EarlyJojaMembershipDiscountMail.title": "Early Joja Membership Discount",
    "blue704.JojaCC_FarmerBundleBookCaskMail.text": "Dear @,^^Again I would just like to thank you for all of the work that you did completing the Farmer Bundle. Thanks to you I can spend some time cooking for the community and sharing the recipes that have been passed down to me from my mother.^^But I have one more small present for you. Mr. Todd said that he was going to build that cellar in the pantry for us and I thought that you might need a few casks to help get you started? These have been gathering dust in our house so I wanted you to have them. Please come my new shop when you have the chance!^^Love, Evelyn",
    "blue704.JojaCC_FarmerBundleBookCaskMail.title": "Farmer Bundle Book Complete",
    "blue704.JojaCC_BulletinBoardComplete.text": "Dear @,^^As you have been completing the Bulletin Board requests, Joja has been shipping the items to the recipients on your behalf and the comments have been overwhelming!^^Every individual has expressed their deepest gratitude towards you for the effort that you have put forth in acquiring these items. So not only do you have my thanks, but I believe you may now be the most popular individual in Pelican Town. Keep up the good work @!^^-Morris",
    "blue704.JojaCC_BulletinBoardComplete.title": "Bulletin Board Complete",
    //Buildings
    "blue704.JojaCC_GeodeCrusher": "Geode Crusher",
    "blue704.JojaCC_GeodeCrusherDescription": "Crushes a large amount geodes every day.",
    "blue704.JojaCC_GeodeCrusherInvalidItem": "Can only process geodes, mystery boxes, golden coconuts, and artifact troves.",
    "blue704.JojaCC_GeodeCrusherChestFull": "Cannot process more geodes. Please empty the chest.",
    //Events
    "JojaCCIntro.0": "Welcome @!$h#$b#Thank you so much for volunteering to help fill the new Joja Civic Center.",
    "JojaCCIntro.1": "As you can see it's already in much better shape than that old run down Community Center, but we still need to fill it with local produce and that's where you come in.#$b#Hopefully then we will be able to entice a few of the local villagers to come open a few shops in here.",
    "JojaCCIntro.2": "I've placed several books around to let you know what is needed, and as you complete the bundles more books will show up for you to complete.#$b#And of course there will be plenty of rewards to compensate you for all of your hard work.$h",
    "JojaCCIntro.3": "Here let me show you around.",
    "JojaCCIntro.4": "Here is what we hope to be a fish pond filled with local fish.",
    "JojaCCIntro.5": "And over here...",
    "JojaCCIntro.6": "What is this?$3",
    "JojaCCIntro.7": "I don't know who placed this here but don't worry. I will get it all sorted out.",
    "JojaCCIntro.8": "Anyway let me show you the pantry as well. It's just over here.",
    "JojaCCIntro.9": "And here is the pantry which we desperately need filled with crops and cooking products so that we can open up the kitchen.",
    "JojaCCIntro.10": "So as you can see there is a lot of work ahead of you, but I'm sure that it will be a very rewarding experience for all of us.$h",
    "JojaCCIntro.11": "Also don't forget to stop by JojaMart and purchase some Communtiy Development projects when you're able to.#$b#With your help JojaMart will really be able to brighten up this small town!$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.0": "Hey @!$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.1": "Did you see our Treasure Hunt bundle in the new Civic Center?",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.2": "Morris was upset that it was there.",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.3": "I did see it, but what is a Treasure Hunt Tag?",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.4": "Who's Morris?$3",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.5": "I think he's that old man that runs the new store?",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.6": "Oh well don't worry about him. Come follow us and we'll tell you everything!$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.7": "Oh it's part of a new game that me and Vincent made up.#$b#Come follow us and we'll tell you everything!$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.8": "Here it is!$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.9": "We put a lot of work into this.",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.10": "Yeah I built the sign all by myself.",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.11": "Would you like to play a Treasure Hunt game with us?",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.12": "Yeah I'd love to guys!",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.13": "I don't know I'm pretty busy around the farm these days...",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.14": "Yes I knew you would play with us!$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.15": "All you have to do is follow the clues on the sign to where another bundle is located somewhere in the valley.#$b#Once you complete that bundle you'll get a special Treasure Hunt Tag that you can bring back here for a big reward.",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.16": "I bet you won't be able to find them all. We hid them real good.",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.17": "The other bundle won't be ready until the next day though!#$b#Give us some time to set it all up.$h",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.18": "Yes!$h#$b#I get to do the first one.",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.19": "Well if you change your mind @ we'll leave it here...$s",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.20": "We worked really hard making this @!$s#$b#If you just try it I know you'll have fun...",
    "TreasureHuntBundleStart.21": "I guess the clues are on my sign if you decide to play our game later...$s",
    "FarmerBundle01Complete.0": "Just now at JojaMart...",
    "FarmerBundle01Complete.1": "What do we have here?#$b#It must be that shipment that I was expecting!$h",
    "FarmerBundle01Complete.2": "Yes! Just what I was expecting.#$b#Pierre thought he had the upper hand but now JojaMart is the only supplier of these premium seeds.$h",
    "FarmerBundle01Complete.3": "Let's see what is in here exactly.#$b#There are garlic, rhubarb, strawberry, blueberry, red cabbage, artichoke, beet, and what else is in here at the bottom?",
    "FarmerBundle01Complete.4": "There are even starfruit and cactus seeds in here!#$b#Haha. Pierre is in trouble now...",
    "FarmerBundle05Complete.0": "Just now at JojaMart...",
    "FarmerBundle05Complete.1": "What is that smell?#$b#It's terrible!",
    "FarmerBundle05Complete.2": "It is coming from the box.#$b#That must mean that it's the shipment of fertilizer I ordered.",
    "FarmerBundle05Complete.3": "Cough.Cough.#$b#It's even worse inside.#$b#I hope this fertilizer sells better than it smells.",
    "FarmerBundle05Complete.4": "Let's see what is in here exactly.#$b#There is some tree fertilizer, some deluxe retaining soil, a little deluxe fertilizer, and what else is that?",
    "FarmerBundle05Complete.5": "There's even some hyper speed gro in here!#$b#I thought that stuff was radioactive...",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.0": "Ah, perfect timing. I see you just completed the Forager Bundle.",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.1": "I was just bringing Leah here to see the new shop that she's opening.#$b#Let's step inside so that Leah can see her new place.",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.2": "Wow this is amazing!$h#$b#Thank you @. I know that it was a lot of work to find all of those things, but I am really grateful.",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.3": "And to show my appreciation me and Morris have a little surprise for you!$h",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.4": "That's right. Leah has discovered a lovely clearing behind the Bus Stop and has asked Joja to open a path so that you can use it.$h",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.5": "You'll love it @! There's even an old shed there that I'm sure you'll find a use for.$h",
    "ForagerBundleComplete.6": "Just give us some time and we'll have it opened right up for you.#$b#I believe we should have all of the work done by tomorrow morning.",
    "ForagerBundleAreaComplete.0": "Early this morning behind the Bus Stop...",
    "ForagerBundleAreaComplete.1": "It looks like they did a wonderful job clearing this pathway yesterday.",
    "ForagerBundleAreaComplete.2": "Leah was right.#$b#This old shed even looks like it's in pretty good shape.",
    "ForagerBundleAreaComplete.3": "I wonder what @ will decide to do with this old place...$h",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.0": "Ah, perfect timing. I see you just completed the Farmer Bundle.",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.1": "I was just bringing Mrs. Mullner here to see the new shop that she's opening.#$b#Let's step inside so that she can see her new place.",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.2": "Oh my goodness this is amazing.$h",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.3": "This kitchen is just so beautiful.$h",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.4": "Thank you @. I can only imagine how hard you worked to stock this kitchen so well.$h",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.5": "But do you know what is missing?$h",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.6": "It would be just perfect if we could have a little cellar inside the pantry over there.",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.7": "You know Mrs. Mullner, I was thinking the exact same thing.$h#$b#Joja's workers are coming today to install one right away. If all goes to plan, it should be ready to age some Joja wine and mead bright and early tomorrow morning!$h",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.8": "Oh my goodness.#$b#It couldn't be more perfect you two.",
    "FarmerBundleComplete.9": "This will be the perfect place to share some of my recipes and my food with the whole town.",
    "FarmerBundleAreaComplete.0": "Early this morning at the Joja Civic Center...",
    "FarmerBundleAreaComplete.1": "It looks like they did a wonderful job building the new cellar yesterday.",
    "FarmerBundleAreaComplete.2": "Just perfect!$h#$b#I'm sure @ will make good use of this place aging lots of Joja wine and mead.",
    "FarmerBundleAreaComplete.3": "Just think of the profits...$h",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.0": "Ah, perfect timing. I see you just completed the Boiler Room Bundle.",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.1": "I was just bringing Clint here to see the new shop that he's opening.#$b#Let's step inside so that Clint can see his new place.",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.2": "I've never seen a boiler room so clean before Mr. Todd. And thank you @ for filling it with all of the things a guy like myself could need.#$b#I've always wanted to move the shop out of my house and this looks like the perfect place for me to set up shop permanently.$h",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.3": "That's amazing Clint!$h#$b#Joja will make sure that you have everything you need here.",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.4": "I was also telling Mr. Todd here about a new cave that I discovered back in the mountains near Demetrius' house.#$b#It had a couple of big rocks inside that my tools couldn't even touch so I asked Morris if JojaCo could break them up for you.",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.5": "We will certainly see what we can do Clint. I haven't heard of anything that JojaCo can't overcome!$h",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.6": "Well even if they can't bust those rocks I'm sure you'll find the old cave useful @. There was even an old machine in there that looks like it was used to crush geodes.#$b#I asked Demetrius to see if he was able to fix it up for you even though it may put me out of business!$h",
    "BoilerBundleComplete.7": "JojaCo plans to get to work right away and we hope to have that cave opened up for you by tomorrow morning so that you can move right on in!$h",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.0": "Early this morning in the mountains...",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.1": "It looks like they did a beautiful job opening up this cave.",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.2": "This must be that old machine that Clint was speaking about?",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.3": "I wonder it's supposed to be used for?#$b#Oh well...",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.4": "They didn't clear the rocks?$3",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.5": "Hmmm...#$b#Well if JojaCo can't bust through them I'm afraid @ will just have to live with it like this.",
    "BoilerBundleAreaComplete.6": "But there should be plenty of ore to mine in here soon anyway!",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.0": "Oh there you are @!#$b#Clint told me that you'd be heading this way.",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.1": "I just finished fixing up this old geode crusher here. It's quite a bit larger than modern day geode crushers but the engineering is just magnificent!$h#$b#It can output over 1000PSI of force and is able to pulverize the densest of materials while still not damaging the valuables inside.",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.2": "I haven't been able to thoroughly test it, but I believe it should be able to process any geode imaginable. Even something like mystery boxes or golden coconuts.",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.3": "And it's easy to operate as well. It functions essentially the same as a mill.",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.4": "All you need to do is place your unprocessed geodes here, and then you can pick up the processed goods on the other side the next day.",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.5": "But that's not all @. Let me show you something else right over there...",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.6": "I'm sure Clint told you about these rocks that his tools couldn't penetrate correct? Well Joja was up here the other night throwing everything they had at them too but look at them now. Not even a scratch...",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.7": "But if you look closely they have been worked on in the past. And there are traces of iridium around them as well.",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.8": "I've heard there used to be a tribe of dwarves that lived in these mountains. I used to think that it was just a myth but this may be proof of their existence#$b#Sadly I don't think you'll be able to delve deeper into this cave unless you somehow become friends with a dwarf...",
    "DemetriusHintsatCave2.9": "Haha! Listen to me.#$b#Friends with a dwarf. What kind of scientist am I? Haha!",
    "DwarfClearsStones.0": "Are those explosions coming from the mountains?",
    "DwarfClearsStones.1": "Ah...",
    "DwarfClearsStones.2": "It has been such a long time since I've been to the surface.#$b#How humans can stand this brightness is beyond me.",
    "DwarfClearsStones.3": "What did @ call them?#$b#Stars?",
    "DwarfClearsStones.4": "There is a certain beauty to them...",
    "DwarfClearsStones.5": "I hope removing those rocks makes @ happy.#$b#It is nice to have a human friend once again...",
    "GoldenBundleComplete.0": "Yesterday afternoon at the Joja Civic Center...",
    "GoldenBundleComplete.1": "Since @ completed that Vault bundle we now have the funds to stock our Prize Machine.#$b#Let's see what Joja sent...",
    "GoldenBundleComplete.2": "Ooohh...#$b#What do we have here?",
    "GoldenBundleComplete.3": "There's some seeds, some fertilizer...",
    "GoldenBundleComplete.4": "And what's this?#$b#An Autopetter!?",
    "GoldenBundleComplete.5": "That'll make someone's day I'm sure.$h",
    "VaultRoomComplete.0": "Ah, perfect timing. I see you just completed the Vault Room Bundle.",
    "VaultRoomComplete.1": "I was just bringing Lewis here to see his new office.#$b#Let's step inside so that Lewis can see his new place.",
    "VaultRoomComplete.2": "An office just for me...$h#$b#I don't know what to say Morris. And of course thank you @ for funding this whole endeavor.",
    "VaultRoomComplete.3": "Joja feels very strongly about the local government officials having a place to manage the town Mayor Lewis. This is the least we could do for you.",
    "VaultRoomComplete.4": "@...#$b#I'm ashamed to admit that I didn't think very much of you when you first stepped off of that bus. I thought you would decide that old farm was too tough and you'd head right back to where you came from.",
    "VaultRoomComplete.5": "But you proved me wrong. You've done more for this town than anyone else, including me.",
    "VaultRoomComplete.6": "But maybe now we can change that!$h",
    "VaultRoomComplete.7": "And Joja is here to stay as well.#$b#We will make Pelican Town a place where everyone can be proud to call home.",
    "FisherBundleComplete.0": "Ah, perfect timing. I see you just completed the Fisher Bundle.",
    "FisherBundleComplete.1": "I was just bringing Willy here to see the new shop that he's opening.#$b#Let's step inside so that Willy can see his new place.",
    "FisherBundleComplete.2": "I didn't know that I'd have my own personal fishin' hole.$h#$b#Did you stock this pond @?",
    "FisherBundleComplete.3": "Yes, @ has been fishing all across the valley and because of ${his^her}$ hard work we now have a fully stocked pond inside the Joja Civic Center.",
    "FisherBundleComplete.4": "Thank you ${lad^lass}$.$h#",
    "FisherBundleComplete.5": "It won't be quite the same as fishin' in the wild waters of the Valley, but I wouldn't mind havin' the chance to fish in the dry on those cold rainy days.",
    "FisherBundleComplete.6": "But the big surprise @, is that Joja is also building a small fish farm near the tide pools for you to use.#$b#Willy was there to advise us on the best way to build without disrupting the enviornment.",
    "FisherBundleComplete.7": "It should be a nice little place for you ${lad^lass}$. This ol' town could use some more fishermen if you ask me.$h",
    "FisherBundleComplete.8": "We have to clear as much of the forage as possible in order to have a place to build the buildings, but it should be ready for you early Sunday morning.$h",
    "FisherBundleAreaComplete.0": "Early this morning at the beach...",
    "FisherBundleAreaComplete.1": "This fish farm is going to be a wonderful addition to Pelican Town.",
    "FisherBundleAreaComplete.2": "Complete with a new shed for @ to use.#$b#I wonder how many Joja Preserves Jars ${he^she}$ can fit in there?",
    "FisherBundleAreaComplete.3": "And the new minecart system should help getting all the way out here too.",
    "FisherBundleAreaComplete.4": "Once again JojaCo has outdone themselves.$h",
    "FirstBundleComplete.0": "Early this morning at the Joja Civic Center...",
    "FirstBundleComplete.1": "Now that @ finished their first bundle it's time I add a few more requests.#$b#Leah asked for several foraging items in order to open up a foraging shop so I'll just place this book here with her requests.",
    "FirstBundleComplete.2": "Now to the boiler room...",
    "FirstBundleComplete.3": "And Clint said that he would like to move his shop out of his house and this would be the perfect place for him to set up.$h",
    "FirstBundleComplete.4": "Of course Clint needs a lot of things in order to set up shop.#$b#Hopefully @ will be able to find everything he needs.",
    "SecondBundleComplete.0": "Early this morning at the Joja Civic Center...",
    "SecondBundleComplete.1": "@ has really been completing those bundles.#$b#At this pace the Civic Center might be finished faster than I ever thought possible!$h",
    "SecondBundleComplete.2": "Now for this bulletin board...#$b#Several of the townsfolk have asked for some rather difficult items and this will be the best place for @ to see what is needed.",
    "SecondBundleComplete.3": "If ${he^she}$ finishes this ${he'll^she'll}$ be the most popular person in town!$h#$b#And now to get the vault ready...",
    "SecondBundleComplete.4": "Mayor Lewis has requested additional funds for the town so I'll just place his ledger book here so that @ can see what's needed.",
